H - 		HEADUP DISPLAY TOGGLE ON/OFF
W - 		WEAPONS DISPLAY ON HUD TOGGLE ON/OFF
SPACE - 	DIFINE OBJECT IN CROSSHAIRS AS PRIMARY TARGET
M - 		MESSAGE SCREEN
