		(SOLAR CHART)

IN GAME (AUTOPILOTS):-
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
1 - MANUAL OPERATION
2 - POINT AT PRIMARY TARGET
3 - PERSUE PRIMARY TARGET
