5 - SLOW THRUST
6 - AUTO FLY AND HALT
7 - POINT IN DIRECTION OF MOTION
8 - POINT OPPOSITE TO DIRECTION OF MOTION
9 - STOP,THEN DROP INTO AUTO PILOT 4
